title: Rainbow Acres
description: Small, well-stocked health food shop. Has a veggie-friendly deli and juice bar with counter seating inside and a couple tables outside. Stocks a range of natural products and natural food, grocery, specialty items. The in-house bakery makes all kinds of sweets and baked goods. Find vitamins and supplements department, bulk staple, snack foods, frozen and refrigerated food, raw food, books, and more. Also another location (much larger) in Marina/Culver area on Washington Blvd near Lincoln.
